snippet.textDisplay: I knew this was coming. In 2019 I wore a mask because of the pollution in the air. Now that everything is open again you can see the pollution again. My daddy was like is it foggy out hear or is it just me? The states with the most factories and stores who push out the most pollution will be attacked the most. I live in Ohio. They coming for us for sure.
